   "id": "F-FIREWALL-GROUNDED",
   "kind": "finding",
   "title": "The LLM-out-of-deduction/decision firewall is theory-aligned (Peirce generation/justification)",
   "statement": "Abduction = hypothesis generation; ranking/testing are deduction+induction. Keeping the LLM out of the deterministic modes is exactly this split \u2014 a feature, not an accident (cf. the IBE conflation).",
